            figures on migration yesterday has been received. In my view&#x2014;I am grateful to the hon. Gentleman for proving that this is correct&#x2014;that evidence proves conclusively that there will not be the flood of migrants from the EU accession states with which we were threatened. One newspaper threatened a flood equivalent to the size of the population of Latvia.
